Croissant Viewer
================

The 🥐 croissant toolbar icon is rendered from Noto Color Emoji, licensed under
the SIL Open Font License, Version 1.1 (https://scripts.sil.org/OFL).
Source: https://github.com/googlefonts/noto-emoji

"Croissant" is an open metadata format from MLCommons
(https://mlcommons.org/croissant). This extension is an independent viewer and is
not an official MLCommons project.
